cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.MM 

Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision): The paper proposes an algorithm for recognizing slab identification numbers in factory scenes using deep learning techniques. 
2. cs.LG (Machine Learning): The paper discusses the development of a deep-learning-based system and the use of weakly annotated ground-truth data to reduce manual labeling work. 
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper proposes a method for integrating and refining information in manual ground-truth data to improve the quality of weakly annotated data. 
4. cs.IR (Information Retrieval): The paper discusses post-processing techniques used to retrieve text information from the modified ground-truth data. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia): The paper deals with image and video processing techniques for recognizing slab identification numbers in factory scenes.
